name: #28. John “Don’t Shoot” Deera
description:
Vegan, pacifist and nature lover. Friend of all creatures. Protector of the forest. 

Special edition bunny: 50% of the proceeds will go to the Bawean Deer Foundation to help protect the Bawean Deer. These beautiful nocturnal deer, endemic to Bawean Island, in Java Indonesia, are listed as Critically Endangered on the IUCN Red List, with only less than 100 remaining in the wild. By purchasing this NFT you can make a real difference.

"What has many teeth, but cannot bite?"
